00:41:13,815 --> 00:41:16,565
Kau yakin dia bisa
membunuh si Hebat...

402
00:41:18,213 --> 00:41:20,440
Mampu membunuh Albus Dumbledore?

403
00:41:21,167 --> 00:41:22,292
Aku tahu dia mampu.

404
