00:42:15,075 --> 00:42:17,825
Matanya bagai Salamander.

416
00:42:18,374 --> 00:42:19,459
Jangan katakan itu.

417
00:42:22,384 --> 00:42:26,575
Katakan saja kau merindukannya.

418
00:42:26,576 --> 00:42:31,063
Kau jauh-jauh ke Paris
